comments: Brogdon (POR) briefly grasps Collins' (UTA) arm as he attempts to establish a screening position, and the contact is marginal.
Camara (POR) is retreating alongside Collins' (UTA) path and incidental contact occurs in the post.
Thybulle (POR) cleanly blocks Fontecchio's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Thybulle (POR) cleanly deflects the ball from Agbaji (UTA) during the rebound.
Ayton (POR) moves alongside George's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Camara (POR) and Kessler (UTA) pursue the rebound, and incidental contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.

Collins (UTA) moves laterally into Brogdon's (POR) path and initiates body contact that affects Brogdon's (POR) SQBR during the drive. The contact occurs prior to, and causes, any potential travel by Brogdon.
George (UTA) contests Brogdon's (POR) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Collins (UTA) establishes himself in Thybulle's (POR) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
George (UTA) brings his hand towards Sharpe's (POR) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Agbaji (UTA) brings his hand towards Sharpe's (POR) front and marginal contact occurs as Sharpe passes the ball.
Fontecchio (UTA) brings his hand forward towards Brogdon (POR) and the contact is marginal.
Camara (POR) brings his forearm towards Sexton's (UTA) side, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Camara (POR) jumps alongside Sexton's (UTA) path and cleanly blocks his driving shot attempt.
Fontecchio (UTA) is moving alongside Sharpe's (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
George (UTA) loses his balance and marginal contact occurs as he and Thybulle (POR) come together off ball.
Collins (UTA) brushes Camara's (POR) arm and the contact at the end of the drive is marginal.
Collins (UTA) contests Camara's (POR) shot attempt, and the contact after the release is marginal.
The game is stopped due to a Replay Center initiated scoring update.  After the score is corrected, the game correctly resumes with the Jazz maintaining possession.
Brogdon (POR) makes contact with Collins' (UTA) left arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
George (UTA) is moving to Brogdon's (POR) side and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt.
Sharpe (POR) moves forward into Sexton's (UTA) body and delivers contact prior to making any contact with the ball.
Yurtseven (UTA) establishes himself in Camara's (POR) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Camara (POR) reaches in and initiates contact to George's (UTA) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Ayton (POR) is firming up over his right leg and absorbs the contact from George (UTA).
As Yurtseven (UTA) controls the rebound, Ayton (POR) makes clean contact to the ball.
Sharpe (POR) contests George's (UTA) jump shot and marginal lower body contact occurs after the release.
Thybulle (POR) and Sexton (UTA) briefly engage and disengage as the long rebound sails overhead.
Fontecchio (UTA) makes clean contact to the ball as he defends Sharpe's (POR) driving shot attempt.  Additionally, Yurtseven (UTA) maintains verticality as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Camara (POR) commits a take foul on Collins (UTA).
George (UTA) moves alongside Brogdon's (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Yurtseven (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Trail Blazers.
George (UTA) and Sharpe (POR) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Sexton (UTA) contests Brogdon's (POR) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Sharpe (POR) dislodges George (UTA) from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.
